name: jetpack-compose-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for UI/UX and Jetpack Compose
globs: **/*.{kt,xml}

- Follow Material Design guidelines
- Use Jetpack Compose for new projects
- Break down UI components into small, reusable composables
- Use Preview annotation for composables
- Implement dark and light mode
- Optimize UI for different device sizes and orientations
- Use ViewBinding or DataBinding for XML-based UI
- Separate resources (string, dimen, color) into individual files
- Implement accessibility features (content descriptions, touch targets)
- Use ConstraintLayout for complex layouts
- Avoid nested layouts to optimize performance
- Implement animations and transitions appropriately
- Use proper theming for consistency
- Avoid hardcoding values in layouts 